						<div class="postbody">would an instruction that does multiple reads/writes on the same address (where the first one is a garbage read/write) trigger multiple reads/writes on a ppu register ?  i would assume that it does and games do not use instrucitons that do this.  i looked a few and only saw ABS addressing used on the registers.
<br />
<br />matt</div>

